Class DclfAlgorithmImpl

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    com.hazelcast.nio.serialization.DataSerializable, DclfAlgorithm, DcLoadflow, IAreaTDFactor, IBranchAngleShiftFactor, IDclfResult, ILineOutageDFactor, ILossFactor, IPowerTDFactor, ISensitivity, NameTag, NetworkRef<AclfNetwork>, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.InternalEObject

    public class DclfAlgorithmImpl
extends DcLoadflowImpl
implements DclfAlgorithm
    DclfAlgo --> AclfNet --> DclfSolver --> AclfNet - DclfAlgo has two ref objects (AclfNet and DclfSolver). DclfAlgo should always go to DclfSolver for data and info, since the data/info might be cached in DclfSolver - DclfAlgo is state-less, meaning the only place to cache analysis result is in DclfSolver

    The following features are implemented:

    • Inject Bus Type
    • Withdraw Bus Type
    • Lodf Analysis Type
    • Withdraw Bus List
    • Inject Bus List
    • Outage Branch List
